Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:13.56,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:311483,313568}Hello? This is Kōda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:15.73,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:313568,315737}Ah! The police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.49,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:316196,318490}No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:20.40,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:318490,320408}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.61,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:320408,322619}Y-Yes, by all means, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:24.45,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:323370,324454}The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:25.24,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:324454,325247}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.24,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:325247,327249}What did they tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:32.17,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:328625,332170}Well, they haven't had\Nany news about Miki yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:35.75,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:332170,335757}It seems they're completely clueless\Nabout her whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:44.84,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:341263,344849}It's all because I had\Ntoo high expectations for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.81,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:344849,346810}That's why… she…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.98,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:353858,355986}Yes, yes, coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:00.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:357862,360031}Good morning.\NHow is Miki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:01.19,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:360031,361199}Oh, about that…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:361199,362867}Did anything happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:07.53,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:364411,367539}Actually, she's gone missing\Ntwo days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:367539,369124}What? She's gone missing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:386349,389185}I didn't know about it at all, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:31.18,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:389894,391187}Oh, Mine-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:33.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:392439,393815}Miki-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.27,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:393815,395275}Yes, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:41.44,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:395275,401448}In fact, this is why we weren't able to attend\Nyour father's funeral. I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:401448,403783}There is no need to apologize, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:46.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:403783,406536}Do you have any idea where\NMiki-san might have gone to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:48.03,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:407329,408038}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:56.96,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:415920,416963}Dear…
