Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.59,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:417964,419591}Someone is calling again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.25,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:419591,421259}Ah… Nozomi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.30,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:422969,424304}Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.93,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:424304,425930}That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:08.68,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:425930,428683}I can barely hear you.\NShimoda Police Department?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.60,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:428683,430602}Miki was found?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:12.27,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:430602,432270}So, is she safe?\NI see. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:433021,434898}Looks like everything\Nwill be fine, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:16.90,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:434898,436900}Yes. Thank you.
