Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.78,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:442822,444783}Thank you very much, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:28.28,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:445658,448286}Did she have an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:33.50,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:450538,453500}They told me that a local fisherman\Nfound her unconscious on the seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:35.33,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:454292,455335}Seashore?…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:456086,457087}Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.79,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:457087,458797}What was she doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:41.63,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:459339,461633}Don't worry, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.80,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:461633,463802}The police said\Nshe didn't have any injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.93,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:465011,466930}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:47.80,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:466930,467806}Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.39,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:468807,471393}I'm going to the hospital in Shimoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:54.31,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:471393,474312}You look very pale, so it might\Nbe better for you to stay at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:58.10,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:474646,478108}No, I'm… I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:01.06,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:478817,481069}No, you can't do it in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.86,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:481069,482862}Let me take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:05.36,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:483947,485365}All right, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:07.36,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:486074,487367}Dear…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:10.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:487367,490995}Sir, maybe I could go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:12.58,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:491538,492580}You want to go, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:17.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:493081,497293}Miki-san is like a sister to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:497293,499087}Please take me with you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:22.21,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:500338,502215}Thank you for your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.84,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:502215,504843}I'm sure that Miki will be\Nhappy to see you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:27.59,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:504843,507595}In that case,\Nlet's go visit her together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.97,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:507595,509973}I don't know how to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:36.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:510598,516229}You don't have to thank me, ma'am, but\NI'm very moved to hear you say these words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:11.05,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:546593,551055}She's been unconscious all the time since\Nshe came here, but it should be all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.05,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:551055,553057}Both pulse and breathing are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.97,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:553057,555977}The electrocardiogram readings\Ndon't show anything out of ordinary, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:18.06,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:557061,558062}Why the bandages?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:20.85,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:558062,560857}Well, she's slightly injured in the head,\Nbut it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.98,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:560857,562984}I see. So she's basically fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.98,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:562984,564986}Yes. Now all that's left\Nis for her to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.61,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:605235,607612}So you're the boy\Nwho's rescued that lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:10.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:609948,610990}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:14.53,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{TIME:610990,614536}Nah, I just saw her when I played\Non the beach and ran to my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:18.24,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{TIME:615620,618248}By the way, miss, you're that singer,\NMine Nozomi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:618248,619832}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:24.00,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{TIME:619832,624003}I knew it! Your "Song of Heart"\Nis something else, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:624003,625630}Really? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.88,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{TIME:626506,628883}I love that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:37.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:636182,637809}Why don't we sing it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:38.76,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{TIME:637809,638768}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.52,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{TIME:638768,640520}But I'm terrible at singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:43.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:640520,643147}It'll be fine. I'll lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:43.89,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{TIME:643147,643898}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.74,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:696618,698745}M-Miki? Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:41.03,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:698745,701039}It's me, your dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:43.04,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:701539,703041}Miki! It's your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:51.54,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:708963,711549}C-Can you recognize me?\NMiki. It's me, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.26,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:717555,719265}Daddy?…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:02.97,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:720141,722977}Miki! Yes, that's right.\NIt's your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.79,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:741954,743790}Nozomi-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:28.71,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:746626,748711}Thank goodness, Miki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.26,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:755551,757261}Nozomi-san…
Comment: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:52.83,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:772835,772835}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:57.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:775813,777482}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:01.06,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:778107,781069}Oh, I wondered who it was,\Nand it was you, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:01.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:781069,781944}Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:02.94,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:781944,782945}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:03.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:782945,783946}It maestro at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:06.32,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:783946,786324}Yes. He's pacing back and forth\Nin the study room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:08.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:786324,788117}Great, I'll go talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:792121,794165}What? A solo show?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.20,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:795166,796209}You heard me right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:19.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:796209,799504}That's fantastic,\Nbut isn't that a bit…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.25,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:799504,801255}…"too early for me",\Nis what you wanted to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:801255,802256}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.71,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:802924,804717}I think the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.17,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:804717,806177}It is a bit early for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.26,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:806177,808262}However, it's not something\Nout of your reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:31.09,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:808679,811099}There are two categories\Nof these shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:34.14,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:811099,814143}The first is when you have worked\Nin the industry for many, many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:38.39,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:814143,818397}and you make such show to, in a way,\Ncommemorate your long career.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:41.81,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:818397,821818}The other one is when you're\Nan ambitious novice who makes up for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:45.23,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:821818,825238}your lack of experience by willing\Nto risk everything to win fast popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:53.53,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:829951,833538}Having said that,\NI'm not interested in either of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:57.54,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:833538,837542}My goal is to make a show\Nwith an artist at the peak of their career.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:04.79,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:838918,844799}I'd like to introduce the public to a singer who\Napplies herself thoroughly at each and every stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:07.92,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:844799,847927}In a way, it's no longer about\NMine Nozomi, the singer,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:11.80,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:847927,851806}but the passion, the emotions, the music itself,\Nlike in your "Song of Heart".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:851806,853683}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:17.35,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:854100,857353}Actually, I was inspired with\Nthis concept by my own master,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:21.73,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:857353,861732}Mr. Yasuoka, one of the greatest music minds.\NHis ambition was to one day make such show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:23.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:862608,863734}Mr. Yasuoka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:26.40,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:864819,866404}Oh, you know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:866404,867905}Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:867905,869282}His name, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:33.28,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:869282,873286}In that case, you'll be happy to hear\Nthat Mr. Yasuoka spoke highly of your song.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:873286,874662}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:36.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:874662,876664}He really did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:38.79,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:876664,878791}He said that if you agreed\Nto make a solo show,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:43.00,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:878791,883004}you could come to influence the direction\Nof music development in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:15:02.06,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:895933,902064}I can't ignore an advice from my old master,\Neven though it's a great test of my own ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:07.02,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:902064,907028}What do you say, Mine? Would you like to work\Nwith me together to pull off the impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:907028,909280}By all means, sir!\NHow could I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.82,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:913659,915828}The show is in October.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:17.45,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:915828,917455}The stage is Kokusai Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:19.49,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:917455,919498}We have a lot of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:20.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:919957,920917}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.00,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:924253,926005}{\i1}Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.71,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:926005,928716}{\i1}My first catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:32.47,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:929550,932470}Hello? Is this Mine Nozomi's\Nfanclub headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.60,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:939393,940603}Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:45.44,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:943189,945441}Over here. Here, look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.44,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:946400,947443}Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:49.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:948361,949570}Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:51.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:949570,951697}When did you start\Nto fix people's roofs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:54.32,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:951697,954325}The matmaker fella let me borrow it\Nfor a while and all's great, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:56.36,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:954325,956369}The damn thing\Nwas leaking like a sieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:58.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:956369,958204}What do you mean, borrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:00.20,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:958204,960206}Come and take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.37,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:961624,963376}How do you like it?\NI'm pretty proud of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:04.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:963376,964460}An office?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:07.79,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:964460,967797}Hehe. We even have\Nour own landline.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:969006,970299}What business are you starting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:11.42,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:970299,971425}This says everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:973427,974720}Kuma-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:17.13,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:974720,977139}"Mine Nozomi's\NFanclub Management Office".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.14,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:977974,979141}How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:981560,982645}Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:27.48,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:984647,987483}There's also one more signboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.65,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:987483,988651}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:989360,990152}Miki-san, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:32.15,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:990152,992154}Mine Nozomi Fanclub Management Office\NKōda Miki Fanclub Management Office{NOTE:峰のぞみの後援会事\\N香田美紀後援会事}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:33.99,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:993155,993990}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.74,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:993990,995741}Speaking of which,\Nyou better hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:38.16,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:995741,998160}She's at your home\Npaying respects to Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:998160,999120}You mean Miki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:39.74,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:999120,999745}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:40.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:999745,1000663}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:47.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005668,1007128}Hello, Miki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:49.13,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007878,1009130}Nozomi-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:53.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011048,1013175}I'm so glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:00.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019223,1020725}Miki-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:05.22,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021559,1025229}She wanted to come here\Nas soon as she was discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:27.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047126,1047960}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:30.25,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049003,1050254}Nozomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.96,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050254,1051964}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:35.80,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051964,1055801}I was so mean to you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055801,1057219}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:39.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057219,1059638}You'd better get well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:44.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060806,1064477}You have to resume\Nyour career as a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.89,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064477,1066896}Congratulations\Non your solo concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:49.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066896,1069857}How do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:52.27,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069857,1072276}Ah, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:55.78,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072276,1075780}It ain't a fanclub\Nfor nothing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.23,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075780,1077239}We have our sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078699,1080034}I bet it was Sune-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:02.53,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080034,1082536}She's our informer, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082536,1084497}Color me surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:08.95,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085998,1088959}Anyway, I don't think it was\Na classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:10.12,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088959,1090127}Right, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.52,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112024,1113526}Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.65,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116112,1117655}Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:40.69,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1117655,1120699}– Good evening!\N– Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:43.11,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120699,1123119}Whoa, a gigantic cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:46.45,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123577,1126455}Behave yourselves, kids.\NWe're guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:49.16,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126455,1129166}Ah, it's so shiny.\NWhat a beautiful plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:54.17,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129458,1134171}It was very kind of Miki-san and your husband\Nto come and visit us the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:58.17,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134171,1138175}No, no, it was nothing, after all the problems\Nwe had caused to poor Nozomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.67,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139510,1141679}I'd like to express\Nmy sincere apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:06.22,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142054,1146225}Oh, there's no need at all.\NAfter all, we're not free of blame, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:08.26,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146225,1148269}May we ask for your forgiveness?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:10.10,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148269,1150104}Naturally. Let's leave\Nthings in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:11.77,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150104,1151772}Congrats.\NGood to see you recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:13.77,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151772,1153774}Thank you, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:18.82,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155317,1158821}All right, everyone. Let's sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:33.83,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170249,1173836}Today is my 58th birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:37.04,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173836,1177047}We'll also celebrate Miki's recovery.\NI sincerely thank all of you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:41.55,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178674,1181552}Miki and Nozomi-san were born\Non the same day in the same hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:46.09,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181552,1186098}This incident seems to have caused much trouble\Nand problems to both of our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:49.31,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186098,1189310}But fortunately,\Nnow we are all reunited
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:53.89,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189310,1193898}and I believe it is appropriate to consider\Nwhat happened as history of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:20:00.07,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193898,1200070}I would like us to get along with each other and\Nconsider our family to have grown a little bigger.
