Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:20.37,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1336457,1340377}{\i1}Thus, the phenomenal vocalist\NMine Nozomi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:23.71,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340377,1343714}{\i1}overcame the first big challenge\Nin the long career she's chosen for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:28.34,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345049,1348344}{\i1}But naturally that was only the beginning.\NLet's remember that just like for this girl,
